    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《绝命荣光：末世之序》是砍杀类的轻度类Rogue硬核作品。这里邪祟丛生，近战搏杀疾如闪电，技能威力强大无比。你会加入一个秘密组织，以超自然现象为调查目标，为人类的存亡舍身战斗。​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266060/extras/27bafcf88c8bbbf0da3baf3f2f58ca17.poster.avif?t=1771923149\" width=612 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266060/extras/27bafcf88c8bbbf0da3baf3f2f58ca17.webm?t=1771923149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >手绘漫画分镜无缝嵌入游戏进程，让你彻底沉浸在诡谲莫测的暗黑剧情中。伴随你的每一局挑战、每一次死亡，恶狼岛内潜伏的危机、潜藏的秘密也将逐步展露出它们的真实面貌。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266060/extras/0a2c54d8f95d2cc80b6d8facc467fd26.avif?t=1771923149\" width=612 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索这座岛屿上的不同环境，通过一轮又一轮的拼杀，逐步揭露绝命荣光这个组织背后的残酷真相。在揭晓秘密的过程中，你将在无名特工和关键特工的身份间切换，跟随他们各自的故事线，你将逐步撕开恶狼岛的骇人真相。​</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266060/extras/35a415c65de4031af17f6c0db84984b0.poster.avif?t=1771923149\" width=612 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266060/extras/35a415c65de4031af17f6c0db84984b0.webm?t=1771923149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有章法的攻击只会加速你的失败。尽情探索技能、神器和恶魔契约的最优组合，找到最适合你的独特战斗风格。直面强大的首领怪物，将你的战斗优势发挥到极致。让敌人尝尝“炼狱”的滋味！ your enemies!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢迎来到《绝命荣光：末世之序》的世界！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266060/extras/c6618fbb74189354a7ee33f71678772d.avif?t=1771923149\" width=612 height=140 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >暴虐严酷的砍杀式轻度类Rogue玩法​</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >粗犷的手绘暗黑时代美术风格与3D场景完美结合</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >环境设定多样，多个可操作关键角色拥有各自的剧情线、技能及玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序生成的游戏流程与剧情无缝衔接，伴你逐步揭开黑暗、血腥、复杂剧情的神秘面纱</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1266060/extras/3fa97e20779bae97fc48ec4846c3fb26.avif?t=1771923149\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
